imdb.plot outline: Daniel and Bradley are best friends and roommates whose success with relations and women -- and relations with women -- is entirely accidental. They each have different intentions and methods to closing the deal, but somehow always manage to get in their own way despite themselves. This is their sad story. But their sad story is funny. Heck, it's funny sad. Don't tell them we said that. They think we're laughing with them.
